 You and more recompensed before You that hasten the acceptance of request, for the sake of Your great hidden name that is honoured, mighty and more splendid. The name You love which pleases You if You are call with it. Thus You answer the call; it is Your responsibility not to prohibit nor reject those that requested from You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَسْاَلُكَ بِاَفْضَلِ الْمَسَاۗئِلِ وَاَنْجَحِهَا وَاَعْظَمِهَا، يَا اَللهُ يَارَحْمَانُ يَا رَحِيْمُ وَبِاَسْمَاۗئِكَ الْحُسْنٰى، وَاَمْثَالِكَ الْعُلْيَا، وَنِعَمِكَ الَّتِيْ لَاتُحْصِىْ۔ وَبِاَكْرَمِ اَسْمَاۗئِكَ عَلَيْكَ، وَاَحَبِّهَا اِلَيْكَ، وَاَقْرَبِهَا مِنْكَ وَسِيْلَةً، وَاَشْرَفِهَا عِنْدَكَ مَنْزِلَةً، وَاَجْزَلِهَا لَدَيْكَ ثَوَابًا، وَاَسْرَعِهَا فِي الْاُمُوْرِ اِجَابَةً وَبِاسْمِكَ الْمَكْنُوْنِ الْاَكْبَرِ الْاَعَزِّ الْاَجَلِّ الْاَعْظَمِ الْاَكْرَمِ، اَلَّذِيْ تُحِبُّهُ وَتَهْوَاهُ، وَتَرْضٰى بِهِ عَمَّنْ دَعَاكَ، فَاسْتَجَبْتَ لَهُ دُعَاۗءَهُ، وَحَقٌّ عَلَيْكَ اَنْ لَاتَحْرِمَ سَاۗئِلَكَ وَلَاتَرُدَّهُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10"